{"tid":1754003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立淺藍淺黃文宣隊","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:32:24.000Z","uid":3280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"111a0d02da3e33da83fe494f9dfd9ec1c5e152ef","tid":1754003,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"目標群組： 淺藍黃<br />\n<br />\n手法：一切可行方法<br />\n包括 街招 入藍group whatsapp文宣 facebook文宣<br />\n面對淺藍親友對答指藍<br />\n<br />\n大方向<br />\n1. 唔講高尚理念 講經濟民生<br />\n2. 唔講港獨本土 講愛國不愛黨<br />\n3  唔講勇武抗爭 講和理非遊行<br />\n4 唔大力屌鳩 要日日煩鳩佢地洗佢地腦<br />\n<br />\n要收集下淺藍絲既理念 再諗教育方法<br />\n洗腦指南<br />\n<br />\n藍親戚：我都支持民主 不過搞到交通民生就唔岩la<br />\n<br />\n大家可以集思廣益"},{"pid":"99fa5c3741c700a177ab9d2a3b91706d9b3c2188","tid":1754003,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=35e0000a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"007851b95b99b10d7c18db0e03e6b00d74cc6c41","tid":1754003,"uid":3280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0547bb609216a17739d89448f47569f65fbfb3","tid":1754003,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac